{
  "page": "Sorrows",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Free_Cities.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Sorrows is located in Free Cities\"><img alt=\"Sorrows is located in Free Cities\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Free_Cities.png/300px-Free_Cities.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"417\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Free_Cities.png/450px-Free_Cities.png 1.5x, /images/a/a3/Free_Cities.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 63.9%; left: 68.1%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Sorrows\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Sorrows</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">Western <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> and the location of the Sorrows\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Sorrows</b> is a stretch of the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoyne\" title=\"Rhoyne\">Rhoyne</a> from south of <a href=\"/index.php/Dagger_Lake\" title=\"Dagger Lake\">Dagger Lake</a> to beyond the ruins of <a href=\"/index.php/Chroyane\" title=\"Chroyane\">Chroyane</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_sorrows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_sorrows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is full of fog and inhabited by <a href=\"/index.php/Stone_men\" title=\"Stone men\">stone men</a> afflicted with <a href=\"/index.php/Greyscale\" title=\"Greyscale\">greyscale</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#About\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">About</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Chapters_that_take_place_in_the_Sorrows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chapters that take place in the Sorrows</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"About\">About</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sorrows&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: About\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:In_the_sorrows_MarcSimonetti.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/In_the_sorrows_MarcSimonetti.jpg/350px-In_the_sorrows_MarcSimonetti.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"347\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/e/ec/In_the_sorrows_MarcSimonetti.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:In_the_sorrows_MarcSimonetti.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The <i><a href=\"/index.php/Shy_Maid\" title=\"Shy Maid\">Shy Maid</a></i> passing through the Sorrows - by Marc Simonetti ©</div></div></div>\n<dl><dd><i>See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_the_Sorrows\" title=\"Category:Images of the Sorrows\">Images of the Sorrows</a></i></dd></dl>\n<p>The fog of the Sorrows is attributed to the fall of <a href=\"/index.php/Chroyane\" title=\"Chroyane\">Chroyane</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Garin%27s_Curse\" title=\"Garin&#39;s Curse\">Garin's Curse</a> upon the <a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_Freehold\" title=\"Valyrian Freehold\">Valyrians</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Spice_War\" title=\"Second Spice War\">Second Spice War</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> There has not been law above the Sorrows for a thousand years, so <a href=\"/index.php/Pirates\" title=\"Pirates\">pirates</a> are common in the Rhoyne north of Chroyane, although they do not enter the ruined city.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/Volantis\" title=\"Volantis\">Volantene</a> galleys patrol the river south of the Sorrows.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> The <a href=\"/index.php/Shrouded_Lord\" title=\"Shrouded Lord\">Shrouded Lord</a> is said to rule the Sorrows.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sorrows&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sorrows&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a> travels with the crew and passengers of the <i><a href=\"/index.php/Shy_Maid\" title=\"Shy Maid\">Shy Maid</a></i> through the Sorrows. In <a href=\"/index.php/Chroyane\" title=\"Chroyane\">Chroyane</a> they are attacked by <a href=\"/index.php/Stone_men\" title=\"Stone men\">stone men</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sorrows&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>There is no law above the Sorrows, not for a thousand years.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Yandry\" title=\"Yandry\">Yandry</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">Tyrion Lannister</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chapters_that_take_place_in_the_Sorrows\">Chapters that take place in the Sorrows</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sorrows&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Chapters that take place in the Sorrows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_18\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 18\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i>: 18. Tyrion V</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sorrows&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiaf_sorrows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiaf_sorrows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  Sorrows.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd18.7B.7B.7